headline: Microsoft earnings, Fed decision, Trump-Xi meeting: What to Watch
summary: Market Domination Overtime host Josh Lipton previews several of the biggest stories to come tomorrow, Wednesday, October 29, including the Federal Reserve's latest decision around interest rates; earnings from Magnificent Seven tech companies Alphabet (GOOG, GOOGL), Meta Platforms (META), and Microsoft (MSFT); and President Trump's meeting with his Chinese counterpart, President Xi Jinping, in South Korea. To watch more expert insights and analysis on the latest market action, check out more Market Domination Overtime.
